[color=#ffff00][center]Mods needed for you to have the exact look of my character.[/center][/color][/size][/font][center]
[url=http://www.loverslab.com/topic/5426-flans-eyes-for-skyrim/]Flan's Eyes for Skyrim

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/45641/?]Ravens Warpaint[/url]

[size=3]I really recommend you to use ~[/size][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52841/?]Freckle Mania[/url][size=3]~!



FOR ALL WHO ARE HAVING PLOBLEMS WITH PURPLE TEXTURE, JUST GO ON THE BODY PAINT ABA, FOOT PAINTS, HAND PAINTS, AND FULLY CLEAN ANY PAINT THAT HAS THERE!!!!!![/size]



[color=#00ff00][size=4]>>>>>Do not forget to send me screenshots of how she got into your game!<<<<<[/size][/color]



[img]http://i.imgur.com/dtue1Pk.jpg[/img][/center]

[center][color=#00ff00][size=4]Installation and how to use:[/size]
[/color][size=3]Just put "Tyerine.jslot" in: C:\Program Files\The Elder Scrolls V Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
[/size][color=#00ff00][size=4]In game:[/size][/color] open the Racemenu, Select Nord Race, go to the Presets tab, press "F9" and select Tyerine.jslot!


[color=#cc0000][size=3]Mods used in screenshots:
[/size][/color][size=4][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52711/?]Dragonbone Barbarian Armors[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12092/?]Cloaks of Skyrim[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/74579/?]Linkle Outfi[/url] (Necklace)
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35056/?]Facial Piercings[/url][/size]
